articles.author: Jenni Reid
articles.title: Covid vaccine rollout begins early in the UK with new variant under watch - CNBC
articles.description: The National Health Service wants to avoid another "twindemic" of Covid and flu putting strain on hospitals.
articles.content: LONDON England on Monday began its winter Covid-19 and flu vaccination campaign ahead of schedule as it monitors a new variant and seeks to avoid another "twindemic" straining the health-care system.… [+3315 chars]
